{"tid":245385,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「無聊一問」借錢俾人，佢有心唔還，可唔可以告佢","createTime":"2017-05-16T07:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T02:38:31.000Z","uid":49369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a872688ebeb71cb74872ea4dce0b37136967767","tid":245385,"uid":49369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T07:57:25.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以解答？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb2d97b7990c0eea497fbff5446153fcc267d4c","tid":245385,"uid":4179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T07:57:47.000Z","msg":"無架喇"},{"pid":"103d555c6fe18409eb791c35d1961bf1090935d3","tid":245385,"uid":20653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T07:58:09.000Z","msg":"人地憑自己能力借返黎架"},{"pid":"dc42c484d87fc085dbca316d716c44cf306d5663","tid":245385,"uid":49369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:01:58.000Z","msg":"真係嫁，原本追佢還，諗住佢態度好啲唔還都可以，但係佢就覺得我叫佢還錢係我既錯咁，真心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fbdb99d6c171fc2467ea11cec8cd31bb391acd0","tid":245385,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:06:20.000Z","msg":"借到錢係佢本事，做咩要還"},{"pid":"9d0a16d8281414d3f726bb686b0124197024f6d8","tid":245385,"uid":49369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:07:36.000Z","msg":"算啦，就怪自己傻仔，太過好人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910339bef353b647fce6427b28a982e2ab9b9b43","tid":245385,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:11:25.000Z","msg":"呢個世界大把陷家鏟, 唔還你老母借銀行點解搞鳩平民."},{"pid":"42c50e3458bae0ce80179f42ce9c9ff6629db4d4","tid":245385,"uid":6329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:15:26.000Z","msg":"幾多錢？"},{"pid":"226626a97875fec530bf774faff4c6ca70383e74","tid":245385,"uid":49369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:17:57.000Z","msg":"一張金牛，佢一開頭重要問我借3張，好彩我淨係借左一張"},{"pid":"d61eda7f4fce61ef6db9758d253aa25d597b373e","tid":245385,"uid":94176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:30:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/civilCase/start_civil_action/q2.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2FcivilCase%2Fstart_civil_action%2Fq2.shtml&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=0ec570e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/civilCase/start_civil_action/q2.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n 小額錢債審裁處會處理甚麼民事案件？<br />\n<br />\n小額錢債審裁處以快速、簡單、且花費不多的形式，處理不超過5萬元的申索。小額錢債審裁處雖屬法庭，卻毋須像其他法庭一樣嚴格依循證據法規則。再者，當事人不可由律師代表出庭應訊，但他們可於出席聆訊前諮詢律師。<br />\n<br />\n小額錢債審裁處主要處理以下幾類申索︰<br />\n<br />\n債務追討；<br />\n服務費的追討；<br />\n涉及財物損毁的申索；<br />\n涉及已售貨物的申索；<br />\n消費者提出的各種申索（可於另一題目（消費者投訴）獲取進一步資料）。<br />\n不過，小額錢債審裁處並不受理下列申索︰<br />\n<br />\n工資；<br />\n土地收回（可於另一題目 ( 業主與租客) 獲取進一步資料）；<br />\n贍養費（可於另一題目 ( 婚姻及家庭事宜) 獲取進一步資料）；<br />\n永久或短暫形式的誹謗（可於另一題目 ( 誹謗) 獲取進一步資料）。<br />\n假如申索額超過5萬元，你不得將其分拆為多宗個案辦理，並使每宗個案的申索額不超過 5 萬元。但你可以放棄超額部分，以便提出一項5萬元以內的申索。<br />\n<br />\n如我決定在小額錢債審裁處提出申索，該怎麼辦？<br />\n<br />\n如欲了解更多關於在小額錢債審裁處提出申索的所需文件、費用和聆訊程序，請瀏覽司法機構的網頁。<br />\n<br />\n有關如何準備出庭應訊（從訴訟雙方之角度看），請登入此處。"},{"pid":"ee0c30a681bd41d9b92c051a5815fa4d2fefee98","tid":245385,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:41:10.000Z","msg":"佢憑自己能力本事借返黎點解要還？"},{"pid":"2cb7ebafe5457c137f152140a9f4d20233515595","tid":245385,"uid":49369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢憑自己能力本事借返黎點解要還？</blockquote><br />\nChing 我都知自己傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a08016c20a45792aeac66ed56bad0cf1ef327ee","tid":245385,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:48:51.000Z","msg":"有冇證據？"},{"pid":"9dc950b4f79e2c9503867420236ada0e80356f4d","tid":245385,"uid":49369,